      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;hpe-pdu-admin-procedures&#34;&gt;HPE PDU Admin Procedures&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The following procedures are used to manage the HPE Power Distribution Unit (PDU):&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-16/operations/hpe_pdu/hpe_pdu_admin_procedures/#verify-pdu-vendor&#34;&gt;Verify PDU vendor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-16/operations/hpe_pdu/hpe_pdu_admin_procedures/#connect-to-hpe-pdu-web-interface&#34;&gt;Connect to HPE PDU web interface&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-16/operations/hpe_pdu/hpe_pdu_admin_procedures/#hpe-pdu-initial-set-up&#34;&gt;HPE PDU initial set-up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-16/operations/hpe_pdu/hpe_pdu_admin_procedures/#update-hpe-pdu-firmware&#34;&gt;Update HPE PDU firmware&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-16/operations/hpe_pdu/hpe_pdu_admin_procedures/#change-hpe-pdu-user-passwords&#34;&gt;Change HPE PDU user passwords&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/docs-csm/docs-csm/en-16/operations/hpe_pdu/hpe_pdu_admin_procedures/#discover-hpe-pdu-after-upgrading-csm&#34;&gt;Discover HPE PDU after upgrading CSM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMPORTANT:&lt;/strong&gt; Because of the polling method used to process sensor data from the HPE PDU, telemetry data may take up to six minutes to refresh; this includes the outlet status reported by the Hardware State Manager (HSM).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
